            <p class="card-text">You can create users, properties, contracts and many more options to have total control of your business.</p>
            <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">See more...</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <img class="card-img-top" src="~/images/l5.jpg" alt="Card image">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h4 class="card-title"><b>Manage your leased properties</b></h4>
            <p class="card-text">With this application, you can manage the properties you have for rent and their respective contracts.</p>
            <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">See more...</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <img class="card-img-top" src="~/images/l6.jpg" alt="Card image">
        <div class="card-body">
